description: This file is the entry point for a React web application, responsible for rendering the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It imports React libraries, styles, and the main App component, then initializes and renders the application.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React node for rendering the React component tree.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the DOM.
